  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="Aink101-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">
            tāykku uraitta pattu </p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">
The ten that was narrated to the Mother
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Aink101">
            <lg type="edition">
              <l> aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai yutukkā </l>
              <l> ṇērkoṭip pācaṭumpu pariyavūr piḻipu</l>
                        <l> neytaṉ mayakki vantaṉṟu niṉmakaḷ</l>
                        <l> pūppō luṇkaṇ marīiya</l>
                        <l> nōykkumarun tākiya koṇkaṉ ṟērē </l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l> Oh mother, please mother </l>
<l> Look there! </l>
<l> As the rising creepers of the green Aṭumpu are torn up </l>
<l> Rising and falling, </l>
<l> Having made the Neytal plant fall </l>
<l> The chariot of the sea-man that is the antidote </l>
<l> To the affliction that is set into the flower-like, kohled eyes </l>
<l> Of your daughter </l>
<l> Has come. </l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
